{"type":"message","id":"972a297d","parentId":"1ac48392","timestamp":"2026-02-17T18:14:52.699Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Tue 2026-02-17 20:14 GMT+2] OPERATION: TSA UPGRADE (THE ARCHIVIST).\n\n1.  **Model Discovery:**\n    *   *Scan:* Check `openclaw.json` or `agents_list` for `gemini-1.5-pro` availability.\n    *   *Decision:* If available, assign as \"Observer-Archivist\". If not, fallback to `gemini-3-flash` with aggressive summarization prompt.\n\n2.  **Protocol Update (Section 15):**\n    *   Edit `docs_archive/MASTER_PROTOCOL.md`.\n    *   *Add Section 15:* \"Hierarchy of Mind (TSA)\".\n    *   *Roles:*\n        *   **Pro (Architect):** Strategy & Code.\n        *   **Flash (Exec):** Fast checks.\n        *   **Archivist (1.5 Pro):** Deep Log Analysis (1M context).\n\n3.  **Infrastructure (`log_compressor.py`):**\n    *   Create `scripts/log_compressor.py`.\n    *   *Logic:* Read `logs/*.log`. Dedup lines. Limit to last 50k chars if model context allows.\n    *   *Output:* `logs/compressed_context.md`.\n\n4.  **Reporting:**\n    *   Confirm Archivist model selection.\n    *   Confirm Protocol update.\n    *   Confirm Script creation."}],"timestamp":1771352092697}}
